alogue, and to civic and religious life.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Mrz 2024) 0aConfucianism. 4aAsian Studies : Asian Religion and Philosophy. 4aAsian Studies : Asian Studies. 4aAsian Studies : Confucianism. 4aPhilosophy : Comparative Philosophy. 4aPhilosophy : Philosophy. 7aRELIGION / Confucianism.2bisacsh40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978143847550940uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781438475509423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781438475509/original  aGBV-deGruyter-alles